  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cherry and cook until the liquid has evaporated, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken broth, honey, cinnamon, and ginger, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, uncovered, for 10 minutes.",
    "While the filling is cooking, prepare the couscous according to the package instructions.",
    "Transfer the couscous to a large bowl and fluff with a fork.",
    "Add the filling to the couscous and toss to combine.",
    "Serve the couscous in a bamboo steamer, garnished with chopped almonds.",
    "Serve immediately, hot and steaming."
